name: Backbone.Factory
description: Backbone.Factory is an extension to the Backbone framework. It's used as an alternate method of creating Backbone collections, models, views, and routers with the purpose of automatically adding user defined properties to these objects.

name: craigmaslowski.com
description: All the source code for craigmaslowski.com which was built using Node.js, Express, Jade, Stylus, Backbone, and jQuery

name: cupboard
description: A windows dev util to create a JS file of client side templates sourced from a folder on the server.

name: ElCacheo
description: Experienced JavaScript developers know that traversing the DOM is an expensive operation which is alleviated by caching commonly used lookups. ElCacheo is a library which makes it easy to cache jQuery or Zepto lookups.

name: FakeServer
description: Fake Server is a bridge between Jasmine and Sinon. It provides a simplified interface for mocking ajax requests with Sinon's fakeServer when writing tests with Jasmine.

name: Grunt-Tutorial
description: The demo project that accompanies my "Understanding Grunt" tutorial

name: meteor-autoform
description: A smart package for Meteor that adds handlebars helpers to easily create basic forms with automatic insert and update events, and automatic reactive validation.

name: microscope
description: Demo app from Discover Meteor book, modified by me to more closely reflect Reddit's functionality.

name: NhlStandingScraper
description: Simple util to scrape the standings on NHL.com and output markdown for updating the sidebar on /r/PacificDivision

name: Objectify
description: Objectify is a node.js module which walks a directory of text files and creates an object based on the directory and files names. The contents of each text file are loaded into properties on the returned objects.

name: Plates-Cupboard
description: Cupboard is an extension to Flatiron Plates templating library. It will recurse through a folder creating an object tree which matches the directory layout. All html files will be loaded from disk, and plates map and bind function become available on the returned objects.

name: SharpRepository
description: C# Generic Repository for use with Entity Framework, RavenDB and more with built-in caching options.
